## ğŸ” Autonomy Levels (Per Module or Task)

| Level         | Description                                                    | Default For           |
|---------------|----------------------------------------------------------------|------------------------|
| ğŸŸ¢ Full Auto   | Agent acts without user approval, but logs all actions        | Low-risk writing tasks |
| ğŸŸ¡ Semi-Auto  | Agent drafts/suggests, user must approve to proceed            | Pricing, narratives    |
| ğŸ”´ Read-Only   | Agent only analyzes, never acts or changes data               | Compliance Checker     |

